<h2>Copperleaf Senior Living works with the most dedicated and committed caregivers in the industry.</h2>
<!--<h3>This is a Heading 3</h3>-->
<br>
<p>Copperleaf Management Group looks for exceptionably personable and dedicated people to join us. Possible positions available are: Resident Care Directors, Resident Care Assistants, Medication Technicians, Activities Coordinators, and Cooks. Experience is good, but more important is your ability to respectfully serve others, make new friends, courteously help those who need help, and support your co-workers.</p>
<p>Please call our Human Resources Department at 715 347-4999 to schedule an interview.</p>
<p>You may fill out the application form below or download our application here: Copperleaf Employment Application</p>

<p><strong>Download Instructions</strong></p>
	<ol>
		<li><span style="font-size:14px;">Download the application.</span></li>
		<li><span style="font-size:14px;">Save it to your PC.</span></li>
		<li><span style="font-size:14px;">Complete the application, and save it again.</span></li>
		<li><span style="font-size:14px;">Email the application you saved as an attachment to <strong>human.resources@copperleafcare.com</strong> or print and fax it to our main business office at 715 343-8863.</span></li>
	</ol>

